| scheduler | device, models | Scheduler, Clock |
| models | (math, time only) | Model interface, implementations |
| device | memory, models | Device, Behavior |
| memory | (encoding, sync) | MemoryImage, Quality |

---

## Key Interfaces

```go
type Model interface {
    ID() ModelID
    Type() string
    Tick()
}

type Device struct {
    id      DeviceID
    typeName string
    mem     *MemoryImage
    behaviors []Behavior
}

type Behavior interface {
    ID() string
    Attach(d *Device)
    Tick()
}
```

---

## Execution Order

1. Models tick (physics)
2. Devices tick (observe models)
3. Clock advances

