## Tick Loop

```
Scheduler.tick()
     │
     ├──► Models[0..N].Tick()
     │         │
     │         └── Evolve physics
     │
     ├──► Devices[0..N].Tick()
     │         │
     │         ├──► Behaviors[0..N].Tick()
     │         │         │
     │         │         ├── Read Model
     │         │         ├── Update Memory
     │         │         └── Return
     │         └── Return
     │
     └──► Clock.Advance()
```

---

## State Transitions

### Runtime States
```
Created → Configured → Running → Stopped → Destroyed
```

### Device States
```
StateCreated → StateInitialized → StateRunning → StateStopped → StateDestroyed
```

---

## Determinism

The runtime is **deterministic**:
- Fixed tick interval
- Models tick before devices
- Devices tick in registration order
- No external dependencies

